The paper discusses the use of artificial neural networks for relation extraction in scientific articles, which falls under the category of natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of convolutional neural networks is a common technique in machine learning (cs.AI, cs.LG), and the task of relation extraction involves identifying patterns and connections between concepts (cs.IR, cs.NE).
